<pb n="0134b" ed="A" xml:id="A112.1494.0134b"/>
<lb n="0134b01" ed="A"/>漢具德經》。</p>
<lb n="0134b02" ed="A"/><p xml:id="pA112p0134b0201" style="margin-left:2em">凡一十六部，三十
<lb n="0134b03" ed="A"/>一卷。</p></item>
<lb n="0134b04" ed="A"/><item xml:id="itemA112p0134b0401"><p xml:id="pA112p0134b0401">小乘律</p>
<lb n="0134b05" ed="A"/><p xml:id="pA112p0134b0501" style="margin-left:1em">自《沙彌十戒儀則經》至
<lb n="0134b06" ed="A"/>《目連所問經》。</p>
<lb n="0134b07" ed="A"/><p xml:id="pA112p0134b0701" style="margin-left:2em">凡四部，四卷。</p></item>
