<lb n="0135b01" ed="A"/>緫八十三部，一百七十
<lb n="0135b02" ed="A"/>卷，<note n="0135b0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【金藏】</note><app n="0135b0201"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【金藏】">巳</rdg></app>編入前錄。</p>
<lb n="0135b03" ed="A"/><list><item xml:id="itemA112p0135b0301"><p xml:id="pA112p0135b0301">大乘經</p>
<lb n="0135b04" ed="A"/><p xml:id="pA112p0135b0401">自《大愛陀羅尼經》至《祕
<lb n="0135b05" ed="A"/>密相經》。</p>
<lb n="0135b06" ed="A"/><p xml:id="pA112p0135b0601" style="margin-left:1em">凡四十部，一百七卷。</p></item>
<lb n="0135b07" ed="A"/><item xml:id="itemA112p0135b0701"><p xml:id="pA112p0135b0701">大乘律<note place="inline">闕</note></p><p xml:id="pA112p0135b0705" cb:place="inline">大乘論</p></item>
<pb n="0136a" ed="A" xml:id="A112.1494.0136a"/>
<lb n="0136a01" ed="A"/><item xml:id="itemA112p0136a0101"><p xml:id="pA112p0136a0101">大乘論</p>
