<lb n="0136a07" ed="A"/>志經》。</p>
<lb n="0136a08" ed="A"/><p xml:id="pA112p0136a0801" style="margin-left:2em">凡二十八部，三十
<pb n="0136b" ed="A" xml:id="A112.1494.0136b"/>
<lb n="0136b01" ed="A"/>八卷。</p></item>
<lb n="0136b02" ed="A"/><item xml:id="itemA112p0136b0201"><p xml:id="pA112p0136b0201">小乘律一部，一卷。</p>
<lb n="0136b03" ed="A"/><p xml:id="pA112p0136b0301" style="margin-left:1em">《解夏經》。</p></item>
<lb n="0136b04" ed="A"/><item xml:id="itemA112p0136b0401"><p xml:id="pA112p0136b0401">小乘論<note place="inline">闕</note></p></item>
